Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:03.99,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,The festival was wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:07.04,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Nishimi-san, I'd love to \Nhear you play the piano again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.13,Main Dialog,Girl 3,0000,0000,0000,,Let me hear it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.27,Main Dialog,Girl 4,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a persimmon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:09.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.19,Main Dialog,Photography Club,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the photography \Nclub! Let me get a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.09,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Stand next to each other, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:16.83,Main Dialog,Boy 1,0000,0000,0000,,This is the birth of the \Nlegendary duo of East High!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.79,Main Dialog,Photography Club,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stand closer to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:20.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:21.95,Main Dialog,Photography Club,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.60,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when did you two become friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.72,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:28.97,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}How do you play in such perfect unison?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:31.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen... Let's get out of here. \NWhen I count to five, run left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:31.47,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You don't have to hide anything from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:33.47,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:32.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,5...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:33.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,4...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:34.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:35.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:36.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.76,Main Dialog,Photography Club,0000,0000,0000,,They're escaping again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:39.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:44.60,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:48.99,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. The girls were supposed \Nto be chasing after us...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:51.66,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, those guys are \Njust like the Beatles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.07,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I've learned from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.24,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about next year's festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.62,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking even further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:03.64,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go so far that they'll \Nnever be able to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.51,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:16.00,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I forget what I was like before I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:20.41,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind caresses my cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:22.74,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,♪Lullaby of Birdland♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:27.31,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick my heels going down the slope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.73,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,As my worthless shadow grows　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:35.84,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an endless summer vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:41.54,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like sneakin' into the swimming pool
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:47.60,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's swim with our clothes on, jump in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:50.27,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A shocking seductive spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:54.77,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This beat that pierces my heart is strange　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.18,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(It flares up, then vanishes)　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.37,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Every miserable day is swell,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:01.31,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,dress it up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:04.90,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A high-speed swing surrounds us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:08.88,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(What's this dance called? I can't stop)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:12.96,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you go, it's twined around my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:18.14,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,and won't leave me ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.42,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.90,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,...is like love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Pops! Sorry I haven't been coming recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:43.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's not here. Maybe in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen... What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:52.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie... Would you check to see \Nif Brother Jun's down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:56.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not summer vacation, \Nso why would Brother Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.72,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a lot's happened while \Nyou boys weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.99,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But he's not here now. He left last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:08.61,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I haven't seen you in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:09.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.38,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Richie-rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.57,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,My piano trio is finally together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:24.44,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi was disowned by his father \Nright after he came back this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.79,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Disowned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:29.79,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, first he went against his parents' \Nwishes by going to college in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.96,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,but then stopped going to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:35.36,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,instead becoming wrapped \Nup in political activism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.54,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,When the prodigal son wandered back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:41.70,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,it's no wonder his dad was furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.57,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi wasn't allowed to set \Nfoot in his family's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:49.74,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,...and soon after, I ran into him \Nat the bar, three sheets to the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.96,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,so I let him take refuge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:53.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my fault Brother Jun left here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:02.47,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. He happened to \Nfind a cheap room to rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.45,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.13,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:12.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Do not mope your life away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:20.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Playing one good session will drive \Naway those blues... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind! Forget I did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:31.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, Mr. Bill Evans, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:35.70,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! What do you say we play a session \Nso I can work off this gloominess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.60,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.98,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.34,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.90,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.68,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,What made him change this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:15.90,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,That one winter day, in the \Nbasement... What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.05,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Did he just do it on a whim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:41.19,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I knock, he may not open the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:50.97,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Or would he look at me again \Nwith those vacant eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.49,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but that doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:10.47,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You win. That angry face of \Nyours is my Achilles heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:14.38,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You had that same expression \Nwhen we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.48,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I remember it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.31,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do? Just go home? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.92,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Mukae-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:45.92,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... Would you give \Nthis to Nishimi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:50.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, wouldn't it be better if \Nyou gave it to him yourself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:54.74,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I couldn't! I'd be \Ntoo nervous! So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:56.93,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:00.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,For me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:05.91,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since the festival, but \Nyour popularity hasn't waned, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What am I staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:28.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What, am I jealous? It has \Nnothing to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.13,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:33.68,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, which scarf design \Ndo you think is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:38.73,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, lately there's \Nthis guy I kind of like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.92,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm thinking about making one for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.15,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:48.67,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,But how about you, Ri-chan? Isn't \Nthere someone that you wanna knit for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.49,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's knit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:56.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have anyone to give it to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:59.39,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, be honest with yourself, Ri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:03.10,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, you were staring \Nat a certain someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.09,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think. \NDon't get the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:10.49,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Nishimi-san \Nis just a friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.34,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful color...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:22.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Kaoru-san would look good in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.65,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:34.17,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me? Why \Nis my heart beating so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.16,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,That day in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.59,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I almost forgot about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.75,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna know why I did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:50.19,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a little too stimulating for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.07,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I was just feeling kind \Nof mischievous at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.43,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:01.94,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:04.19,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come in here because \Nyou wanted me to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:08.44,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What were you hoping for? \NA declaration of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.20,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.45,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the kind of guy I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:21.42,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You've stopped fighting back... \NAre you resigned to it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:22.62,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:26.87,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,"If I act like this, \Nshe'll probably run off."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.09,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:33.83,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.37,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You can do what you want with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:45.78,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, and don't ever come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:48.76,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the same person I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:53.11,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped out of college and \Ngot disowned from my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:57.87,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Society gave me the boot and \Nthere's no way for me to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.08,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Get close to me and your \Nlife will be ruined, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.64,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand what I'm sayin', \Nget the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:18.72,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:22.13,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of you calling me "young lady"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:25.48,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,...so I thought I'd get rid of the \Nimage you have of me as a young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.49,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not the same \Nperson you once were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:34.20,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,...then I can become a new person, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:42.16,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuragi, I'm gonna become a new me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:43.94,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:52.69,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go throwing away something \Nprecious for someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:05.76,Main Dialog,Arita,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Katsuragi-kun \NI've heard so much about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.16,Main Dialog,Arita,0000,0000,0000,,How about saying something \Nto mark the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.02,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.83,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just passing through,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:18.77,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like to share my opinion on \Nwhat a college {\i1}should{\i0} be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:23.03,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuragi... You inspired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:26.12,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Muroi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:30.05,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Listening to your speech made \Nme feel ashamed of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.42,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,for doing nothing but study \Nfor exams and play music.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.51,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Decline of a False System
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:42.51,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Strike Against Rising Tuition
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:42.51,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,All Students on Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:42.92,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Katsuragi, in the next battle, \Nif something were to happen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:47.31,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,would you take over for me, even just for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.86,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Arita-san, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:53.15,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Japan Communist Youth Union
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:12:00.41,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Muroi. Come over once \Nin a while to play the sax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:06.99,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuragi! Arita-san's been arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.49,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,The bones are shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.97,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,so the doc told me my fingers won't \Nbe able to move like they used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.96,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about the sax...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.76,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.25,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so glum, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:33.26,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can dump everything I don't \Nneed and just focus on the movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:37.22,Main Dialog,Muroi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become a new me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:45.90,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:47.91,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:49.95,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:50.91,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:04.72,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna see any more people \Nget hurt because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:12.81,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened to you, \Nand I don't intend to ask about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:18.19,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see that you're hurt deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:23.20,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I support you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.53,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Am I being too pushy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:33.67,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.66,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pushy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.52,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I better stop takin' \Nnaps on the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:59.44,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wasn't that Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.89,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Was she called in by the teacher again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:05.03,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yurika's been acting weird these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.22,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:10.03,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that \Ninnocence she used to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.07,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe something happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.79,Main Dialog,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her that, but she wouldn't answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:19.21,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since she cut her hair \Nlike that, could it mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.41,Main Dialog,Girl 1,0000,0000,0000,,...she's got a broken heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What'd he do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.85,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Sentaro, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.47,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:38.66,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I first met Brother Jun, \Nhe's been like a big brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get good at jazz like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Be strong like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Become cool like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.80,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to follow in his footsteps \Nevery step of the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.28,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...thinking I'd catch up someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.86,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen-boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.71,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Your woman forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:05.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If Brother Jun would just talk \Nto me, maybe I'd understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:12.67,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But if he did something to {\i1}her{\i0}, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brother Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:23.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:38.69,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. He's the one person I didn't \Nwant to find out about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.29,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,But what else could you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.64,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,He was bound to find out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.81,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she was beyond my \Nreach from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... Or I thought I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:17.59,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely, when I'm with Kaoru-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:20.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I can really feel at ease \Nand have a good time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:26.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No. I decided long ago on \Nthe person that I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.97,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:41.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Knitting? Why would she bother hiding that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:47.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:08.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:13.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:17.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're obviously acting strangely \Ntoday. Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I saw 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Saw who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:25.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,When I went to Brother Jun's \Napartment... she was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're sure you saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:34.44,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,And of all people, it \Nhad to be Brother Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's what hurts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothin' I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:50.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were jilted, you've \Nstill got someone who cares for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they say, you can't \Nsee the forest for the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:58.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And those trees are so tall, you must \Nnot be able to see a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:02.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try looking more carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it high time you realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:09.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Figure it out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:17.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You just got here... and \Nyou're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:23.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've got something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done knitting for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I couldn't help \Nglancing at it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:39.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, you're blushing! \NWas I right on the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a min...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this is for the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:55.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have a relapse! \NThis doesn't hurt at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.62,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.38,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You and this man from God knows where...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:10.08,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, you're being tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.10,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:18.02,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth! I'll bring home a \Nsuitable partner for you before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:23.51,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So don't meet with this man again, \NYurika. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:30.02,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, your father is just \Ntalking to you like that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.20,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,because he's worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:38.03,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're a girl, so you have to \Ntake better care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:42.52,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, keep next Saturday open, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:45.60,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I made an appointment for \Nyou at the gynecologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.17,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Are you eating properly? \NA letter came for you, so I'm \Nforwarding it on. \NLove, Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:05.72,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,To My Comrade, \Nfrom Isao Arita
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:18.44,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, that rat... Throws \Nout hints, then goes home...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:23.28,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who cares for me? Like my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what he meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:30.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna be the Virgin Mary
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:32.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,in the Christmas Nativity play, huh, Sa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.97,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But I'm nervous about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hashiguchi-kun will be there to see you too,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so you have to do your best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.87,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't mention him! I don't care if he...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:46.10,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you're the one that said you're \Ngonna marry him when you grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:49.22,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That was a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:54.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sentaro, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:58.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, I wanna get married...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it high time you realized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:28.64,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for you on that slope　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:36.92,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,For our after school promise　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:41.91,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a 'goodbye' blurred far away　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:56.22,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so weak, so awkward, and so fragile back then
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:22:03.77,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,But you gave me a small pair of wings　         　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:09.83,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,In the twilight hour of the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:15.48,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for a gleam of light　　　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:23.45,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could have said that I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:35.72,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The note that I wrote in the corner of my textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:48.80,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,has never been delivered to this day
